38 (b) Each member of the task force who is not a member of the
39 legislature shall represent at least one of the following stakeholders:
40 (1) A Kansas employer with a vested water right;
41 (2) a commercial user of a municipal or industrial water right;
42 (3) an agricultural producer;
43 (4) an economic development organization;

